{"tid":1423983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大學生會會長買雷射筆被捕 警方於警總交代經過","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T16:33:07.000Z","uid":56541,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ce04243b01f9a31ec3be70f3c9eb839ec18c51","tid":1423983,"uid":56541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:11:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ycbO05e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FycbO05e.png&h=caa4f097&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有組織及三合會調查科(O記)總督察<span style=\"color: red;\">周學賢</span>將於今晚10時45分在警總記者會交代詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20150106/large/06ls4p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20150106%2Flarge%2F06ls4p3.jpg&h=762ba289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150106/18992948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150106%2F18992948&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=f9823827\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150106%2F18992948&h=e0c50c14\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150106/18992948</a><br />\n2015年01月06日 <br />\n反東北撥款者 認襲兩警 便衣督察倒地後展示委任證<br />\n去年6月13日立法會財委會審理東北撥款，反對撥款的示威者由中午起陸續抵達立法會地下示威區，有便衣警員在示威區當值，包括港島總區重案2B組主管高級督察<span style=\"color: red;\">周學賢</span>。當晚8時45分，財委會主席吳亮星突「剪布」禁止議員發問，並欲即時表決撥款，示威者情緒變得激動，有人開始衝擊地下大堂公眾入口。<br />\n案情指便衣高級督察周學賢於晚上9時，目睹被告衝向示威區鐵馬並開始衝擊，周向被告表明身份後命令他停止衝擊，再捉住其右臂，其間被告拳打周面部。另一便衣警員見狀上前，表明身份後捉住被告，欲帶他離開示威區，但被告用手肘撞向該警員胸部。"},{"pid":"a2f7744b93b73801850bf3d8c8cb608db1ab6dc0","tid":1423983,"uid":56541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:13:13.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;升咗職喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95f8decd63b1209bfeedffbbe7fdaa7b4d188de","tid":1423983,"uid":56541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d20eb72f3a983fb117240c65188134e57868546","tid":1423983,"uid":56541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f616e5edf7e02f2a4947dd079d07a83412580b","tid":1423983,"uid":101392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:26:22.000Z","msg":"各大專院校天文學會搞全民觀星營有無得諗？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1424020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1424020</a>"},{"pid":"186a0ad7d17c32c472a5cc6ed5bde9ae76fe23c7","tid":1423983,"uid":56541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04b409a44daa15e25032616c5bf85444f54933a0","tid":1423983,"uid":56541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:09:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02575b497b572bfc86ac4bd58ef6d2097fcf6d68","tid":1423983,"uid":56541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:33:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}